snippet.title: Pro Yakyuu Spirits 5 (PS2) - Gameplay
snippet.description: A full game of Pro Yakyuu Spirits 5, a 2008 baseball video game by Konami. This game also came out on PS3, so this is the "old-gen" version. This recording is an All-Star Game, so future MLB stars like Yu Darvish, Koji Uehara, and Masahiro Tanaka all play a role.
